If the Rebel Alliance conducts a successful mission to incite an uprising at one of our systems, or if the number of troops on a system falls below the established garrison requirement, the system is said to be in 'uprising', and all production on that system ceases.   If the uprising is not shortly subdued, facilities on that system may eventually be destroyed, or the system may join the Rebel Alliance.  Uprisings can be subdued by placing twice the normal garrison on the system or by sending a character to perform a 'Subdue Uprising' mission at that location.